,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"點解成堆五毛攪事<br />\n咪就係黨鐵玩完就成堆垃圾都玩完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故形人而我無形，則我專而敵分。我專為一，敵分為十，是以十攻其一也。則我眾敵寡，能以眾擊寡者，則吾之所與戰者約矣。吾所與戰之地不可知，不可知則敵所備者多，敵所備者多，則吾所與戰者寡矣。故備前則後寡，備後則前寡，備左則右寡，備右則左寡，無所不備，則無所不寡。寡者，備人者也；眾者，使人備己者也"},{"pid":"820740d80551cd8343d05b8f00e5bbf9bcd3a261","tid":2128951,"uid":206524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"Melbourne metro真係好垃圾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370e8e2f21a5b4909c96cf603720855d97235fef","tid":2128951,"uid":206524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"820740d80551cd8343d05b8f00e5bbf9bcd3a261","tid":2128951,"uid":206524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"Melbourne metro真係好垃圾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"用慣不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fd982f8c35727777cf1679319ff6fb05b1ddba","tid":2128951,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f41d57de0f4e4d912d5c11a2ecec3bd013b0fd","tid":2128951,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00496dcaa0354c2803efd339b25df1ad120972c7","tid":2128951,"uid":330457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b5d711f013b0c2e98a255f7a7